STEP THROUGH DISASSEMBLY ONE LINE ATA  TIME WITH 'SINGLE STEP'.  BLOADIT      ANYWHERE IN AVAILABLE MEMORYAND CALL   IT.  AT THE PROMPT; ENTERA STARTING    ADDRESS (1-4 HEXDIGITS).'R' RESTARTS THE LISTING.  'S'ALLOWS   YOU TO SPECIFY A NEWSTARTING ADDRESS.  'Q' QUITS.  ANYOTHER KEY DISPLAYS THE  NEXT LINE OFDISASSEMBLY.